urt I&#8217;ve seen. I&#8217;ve always been afraid to try it because it sounded so temperamental. This doesn&#8217;t sound hard at all.. Thanks!</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/07/how-to-make-yogurt/?replytocom=66855#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-66855\", \"66855\", \"respond\", \"13152\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"comment-66866\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/41dc3e007986c35dc46763689fa93174?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.blogger.com/profile/04969442660664176005' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>KWu</a></cite> <span class=\"says\">says:</span>\t\t \t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-meta commentmetadata\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2012/07/how-to-make-yogurt/#comment-66866\">07.16.12 at 5:21 am</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<p>Any thoughts on whether a Dutch oven would incubate as well as the ceramic insert of a slow cooker? I only have a small slow cooker so I&#8217;d be able to fit more jars into the Dutch oven.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/07/how-to-make-yogurt/?replytocom=66866#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-66866\", \"66866\", \"respond\", \"13152\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"comment-66867\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/41dc3e